          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Rule Interpretation & Data Preparation</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-4">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-purple mr-3">•</span>
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium">Scheme Rule Encoding</p>
                <p class="text-grey">Converts natural language scheme rules into precise executable code, identifying ambiguities</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-purple mr-3">•</span>
              <div>
