          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">What is Defined Benefit PRT?</h3>
          <p class="text-grey">Pension Risk Transfer (PRT) for Defined Benefit schemes involves transferring pension liabilities from the original sponsor to an insurer. This complex process requires precise calculation of all member benefits, accurate valuation of liabilities, and careful data cleansing to ensure appropriate pricing and successful transactions.</p>
